00:49:31.980 --> 00:49:35.710
So what is the extent
of the Game of Life?

00:49:35.710 --> 00:49:39.020
What can the Game of Life do?

00:49:39.020 --> 00:49:40.380
It can find prime numbers.

00:49:40.380 --> 00:49:44.730
Actually, speeding up so we have
enough time, the Game of Life

00:49:44.730 --> 00:49:48.640
can do absolutely anything
that any computer can do.

00:49:48.640 --> 00:49:49.140
Right?

00:49:49.140 --> 00:49:52.180
Because what is a computer
at its most basic level?

00:49:52.180 --> 00:49:54.770
It's a bunch of wires with
a pulse going through it.

00:49:54.770 --> 00:49:55.780
It's binary.

00:49:55.780 --> 00:50:00.650
You can emulate a wire with
a pulse going through it

00:50:00.650 --> 00:50:03.200
by a stream of
gliders like here.

00:50:03.200 --> 00:50:04.990
So when there's a
space it's a zero.

00:50:04.990 --> 00:50:06.574
When there's a
glider, there's a one.

00:50:06.574 --> 00:50:07.490
What else do you need?

00:50:07.490 --> 00:50:08.550
You need logic gates.

00:50:08.550 --> 00:50:10.170
You can make the
three logic gates.

00:50:10.170 --> 00:50:12.045
There are patterns for
the three logic gates.

00:50:12.045 --> 00:50:14.900
And you need wires to be
able to cross each other.

00:50:14.900 --> 00:50:17.330
You can do that just by
thinning out the wires so

00:50:17.330 --> 00:50:18.280
they don't hit.

00:50:18.280 --> 00:50:19.690
And you need a memory register.

00:50:19.690 --> 00:50:21.820
You can do that with a
block, which is the square.

00:50:21.820 --> 00:50:24.630
And a block at a certain
distance, keeping the memory.

00:50:24.630 --> 00:50:27.990
So the mathematical
term for that

00:50:27.990 --> 00:50:30.680
would be that Life is
universal because it's

00:50:30.680 --> 00:50:32.510
capable of universal
computation.

00:50:32.510 --> 00:50:36.040
So even though it would be a
very inefficient way to do it,

00:50:36.040 --> 00:50:39.000
you could actually
use the Game of Life,

00:50:39.000 --> 00:50:43.580
which incredibly simple
rules can do anything

00:50:43.580 --> 00:50:47.930
